posting_body: ['$2250 per month includes all.', 'Easy street parking.', 'Charming 1 bedroom/JR 4 (small 2 bedroom connecting) available on the first floor of a Forest Hills private detached house.', 'Master bedroom plus a connecting additional room that can be used as a sunroom/office/guest room/dressing room.', 'Plenty of natural light.', '16 windows.', 'Eat-in-Kitchen includes a dishwasher, refrigerator, stove, microwave and WASHER DRYER.', 'Spa-like bathroom with stand-up shower.', '5 closets.', 'Hardwood floors.', 'Ceiling fans.', 'Wall/ Sleeve air conditioner.', 'VIRTUAL TOUR', 'https://youtu.be/ltIyBJtFwOs', 'Price includes all - ELECTRIC, GAS, heat, water, 940/880 Mbps Fios Gigabit Connection INTERNET, cable box.', "One month security deposit and first month's rent due at lease signing.", '$100 application fee.', 'LEASE START DATE - September 1st, 2022', 'VIRTUAL TOUR address shown above.', 'Viewing by appointment only.', 'For Rent by Owner.', 'Call 7 1 8 8 0 9 0 9 9 7', 'No backyard access.', 'No basement access.', 'No garage or private parking spaces.', 'Easy street parking.', 'First floor only - Approximately 625 sq feet.', 'Non-smokers.', 'No dogs.', '2 blocks outside of Forest Hills Gardens.', 'Close to E, F, M, R trains.', 'Easy street parking.', 'Walk to E, F, R, M trains, shopping and restaurants.', 'LIRR Forest Hills Station - 12 minutes stop to stop to Manhattan.']
